template.name: DroneAbstract

transition.label: x == goal_x && y == goal_y && has_init == true
c = 0

query.formula: // Stay safe, always eventually reach goal
strategy Goal = control: A<> Drone.x == goal_x && Drone.y == goal_y
// Create strategy that minimizes time with regards to the above safe and goal strategies
strategy FastSafe = minE(time) [<=1000] {DroneAbstract.x, DroneAbstract.y } -> {} : <> DroneAbstract.Target under Safe
